    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>类只狼的战斗体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速的攻防节奏。察觉并利用格挡后怪物的攻击间隙进行反击和调整自身状态，结合自身的战斗流派搭建属于自己的爽快战斗体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器解封</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功格挡敌人招式你将获得解封点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/4dbbae3e4ef99273971b4dcda1909983.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=800 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/4dbbae3e4ef99273971b4dcda1909983.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/4dbbae3e4ef99273971b4dcda1909983.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/ae9ca6a9b5d5950e76056b70daa5ea9a.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=800 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/ae9ca6a9b5d5950e76056b70daa5ea9a.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/ae9ca6a9b5d5950e76056b70daa5ea9a.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功破红敌人招式你也能获得解封点</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解封点能干嘛？当然是解开自己的隐藏封印！武器和形象将进入解封形态！大量提升自身性能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/2692ebb548de9552df74794b7b5870b3.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=380 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/2692ebb548de9552df74794b7b5870b3.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/2692ebb548de9552df74794b7b5870b3.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>流派搭建</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢更多危险带来的刺激攻防体验？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是喜欢稳重不断闪避和防御见机一刀结束战斗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亦或者大量刷取顶尖装备，深度了解游戏后在战斗中不断叠加buff硬刚怪物？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这都可以变成现实！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据玩家自己的喜好，通过装备、道具、技能、五行元素四者搭建属于自己的战斗流派<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/69cce2753edb4267b300402002f5e4a3.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/69cce2753edb4267b300402002f5e4a3.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/69cce2753edb4267b300402002f5e4a3.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/86fc09125333cdce19cc82ad4675daa8.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/86fc09125333cdce19cc82ad4675daa8.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/86fc09125333cdce19cc82ad4675daa8.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢乐剧情演出</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天呐，你得爱犬被光明女神诱拐了，你问女神抓你的狗干嘛？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有可能是你的爱狗太威武太雄壮了吧...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管如何，谁抓了你的狗你就得杀了谁！毕竟你是John...是一个白毛女骑士！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后你跟一只一直缠着你的魅魔踏上了寻找爱犬的道路...！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/78802db5a9b68e26f60f52c105ed6122.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/78802db5a9b68e26f60f52c105ed6122.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/78802db5a9b68e26f60f52c105ed6122.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/7bda4ded37aa020bd2edd6a73ed217b0.poster.avif?t=1754645788\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/7bda4ded37aa020bd2edd6a73ed217b0.webm?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244500/extras/7bda4ded37aa020bd2edd6a73ed217b0.mp4?t=1754645788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
